<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bow-n">bow <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /baʊ/    美 /baʊ/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>点头；鞠躬：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He moved aside for her with a polite bow. 
他礼貌地躬身给她让道。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-b">2.★ <strong>/bəʊ/ 弓；弓形物；蝴蝶结：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A violin is played with a bow. 
小提琴是用弓拉的。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Ella wore a bow in her hair. 
埃拉头上戴着一个蝴蝶结。</p></div></div>